Download logo The Minister of Humanitarian Affairs, Disaster Management and Social Development, Hajiya Sadiya Umar Faruq, represented by the Director of Humanitarian Services, Alhaji Grema Ali and the representative of the Director General NEMA, Dr. Nura Abdullahi received the 150 returnees at Malam Aminu Kano International Airport on the 20th day of February, 2023 at 3:45pm.  The movement was facilitated by the Federal Government of Nigeria, Economic Community of West Africa and the IOM. Distributed by APO Group on behalf of National Emergency Management Agency (NEMA), Nigeria.